import React, { useState, useRef } from 'react'; const Slider = () => { const [currentSlide, setCurrentSlide] = useState(true); const sliderRef = useRef(null); const items = ['Item 1', 'Item 2', 'Item 3']; // 슬라이드 요소 const handleClick = () => { if(currentSlide){ setCurrentSlide(false); const scrollAmount = sliderRef.current.clientWidth / 1; console.log(sliderRef.current.clientWidth); console.log(scrollAmount); sliderRef.current.scrollLeft += scrollAmount; return } setCurrentSlide(true); const scrollAmount = sliderRef.current.clientWidth / 1; sliderRef.current.scrollLeft -= scrollAmount; console.log(scrollAmount); } return (
{items.map((item, index) => (
handleClick(index)} // 클릭 시 슬라이드 이동 > {`slide ${index +1}`}
))}
